  "html": "<div class=\"fr-view\"><p>Day 38 - Kanji Practice</p><p>Please download today&#39;s kanji practice here: <a class=\"fr-file\" href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/thinkific/file_uploads/259518/attachments/969/fde/bee/Kanji_Practice_Day_38.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Kanji Practice Day 38.pdf</a></p><p>Practising writing kanji every day is a very important exercise to help you learn quickly. If you have any questions you can always ask other students and teachers in the community <a href=\"https://japaneseonline.gogonihon.com/communities/Q29tbXVuaXR5LTM1MzQ=\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>.</p><p>Refer back to the <a href=\"https://japaneseonline.gogonihon.com/manage/courses/731527/contents/18335052\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Week 8 - Kanji lesson</a> to watch how to do the correct stroke order for 今, 週, 校 kanji.</p></div>",
